## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not account for subsequent developments in the oil market. Additionally, the complexity of global oil markets means that multiple factors can influence prices simultaneously, making it challenging to isolate specific causes. The reliance on secondary sources also means that the findings are contingent on the accuracy and comprehensiveness of the reported information.

